<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>{{.Title}}</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/style.css" />
</head>
<body class="app-body">
  <main class="container py-5">
    <div class="text-center mb-4">
      <h1 class="display-6 fw-bold">图形工具入口</h1>
      <p class="text-muted mb-0">选择需要的图形工作台，上传数据并配置映射后即可生成图表。</p>
    </div>

    <div class="row g-4">
      <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
        <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm border-0">
          <div class="card-body p-4 d-flex flex-column">
            <h2 class="h4"><i class="bi bi-diagram-3 me-2"></i>甘特图</h2>
            <p class="text-muted flex-grow-1">适用于项目排期、里程碑跟踪、计划与实际工期对比。</p>
            <a href="/gantt" class="btn btn-primary w-100">进入甘特图工作台</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
        <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm border-0">
          <div class="card-body p-4 d-flex flex-column">
            <h2 class="h4"><i class="bi bi-bar-chart me-2"></i>通用图形</h2>
            <p class="text-muted flex-grow-1">支持柱状图、折线图、饼图，按字段映射快速生成可视化结果。</p>
            <a href="/viz" class="btn btn-outline-primary w-100">进入通用图形工作台</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
